show.description:
In a remote mountain village, female teachers are being hunted and murdered. When two newcomers arrive, one is haunted by terrifying visions while the other barely escapes the killers’ grasp.
A dark mystery unfolds in a tale of fear, secrets, and the desperate fight to uncover why women are being targeted.
